tool-allocation.layer:

Replaces Framer Motion for simple layout changes.
CSS variables + transition property for sidebar collapse/expand.

Example implementation:
.sidebar {
  width: var(--sidebar-width-closed);
  transition: width var(--duration-medium) var(--ease-standard);
}
.sidebar[data-open="true"] {
  width: var(--sidebar-width-open);
}

Payload: 0KB (native CSS)
